  <summary>Control your AniMe Display graphically on Linux!</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      AniMeGUI is an application for controlling your Zephyrus G14’s AniMe Matrix™ Display graphically on Linux, acting
      as a GUI wrapper for asusctl. Requires asusctl to be installed in the host system and the AniMe Display (only
      Zephyrus G14 laptops)
    </p>

    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Control the AniMe functionalities of asusctl graphically</li>
      <li>Save presets of your favourite animations/images</li>
      <li>Use your webcam (if you have one) and display it to the AniMe display</li>
    </ul>
  </description>

